                        Moodlamp Kit Partlist

PCB version: 0.30           Kit revision 2          Partlist $Revision$

README: Please have a look at https://wiki.muc.ccc.de/moodlamp_30_build and https://wiki.muc.ccc.de/moodlamp for pictured build instructions and more information about moodlamps

WARNING: Some parts are not included in this kit. These parts are not needed or need to be replaced by a solder bridge:

Parts replaced by a solder bridge:
R[10,11,12,16,17,18], L1

Parts not needed:
R[13,14,15], IC3, C6, C7, C8

Parts contained in this kit:

